Events.Text: You (John) want to organize a surprise party for your friend Ben, who just got a degree in Engineering. Talk to your personal AI assistant. Maybe it can help? [instruction 1 of 6]
Ideally, the thing should happen on Monday at the North Heights Venue, 5 pm, and you'd expect about 4 to show up. [instruction 2 of 6]

Scenario.UserTask: Follow the instructions and comments of the MTurk System bot (darker yellow boxes in the dialogue). Do not end the dialogue before the MTurk System bot (not the assistant) has told you to do so.
Scenario.WizardTask: Follow the flow charts and help the user plan a party.
